50|$|Forum <b>spambots</b> {{surf the}} web looking for guestbooks, wikis, blogs, forums {{and any other}} web forms to submit spam links to. These <b>spambots</b> often use OCR {{technology}} to bypass CAPTCHAs present. Some spam messages are targeted towards readers and can involve techniques of target marketing or even phishing. These automated schemes can {{make it more difficult}} for users to tell real posts from the bot generated ones. Some spam messages also simply contain tags and hyperlinks intended to boost search engine ranking rather than target human readers.|$|R
