50|$|Another, more {{malicious}} use of bots is {{the coordination}} {{and operation of}} an automated attack on networked computers, such as a denial-of-service attack by a botnet. Internet bots {{can also be used}} to commit click fraud and more recently have seen usage around MMORPG games as computer game bots. A <b>spambot</b> is an internet bot that attempts to spam large amounts of content on the Internet, usually adding advertising links. More than 94.2% of websites have experienced a bot attack.|$|E
